Since Ultimate Surrender disqualified Devi Lynn from the tournament, Amber Rayne gets the win and moves forward to face Dia "The Iron Maiden" Zerva on July 8th.

We present an exhibition match up and give you a sneak peek at one of next seasons new wrestlers, Jennifer Dark.

Jennifer comes from Hungry, that makes the second wrestler we have hosted from that country. Everyone welcome Jennifer in her debut match up at Ultimate Surrender.
title: SPECIAL EXHIBITION MATCH UP
